               <objectContents>
                  <ab type="description">A man is checking the work material (textile). He has a piece of paper and looks sometime at the paper and sometimes at the material. The pictures are taken from a low angle.</ab>
                  <ab type="comment">Identity in Nas List 1/1970 and Yu Novosti (undated), but it should be notd that they give different information about his place of birth. His position in the factory was warehouse manager. His wife works in the same factory. In Slovenia, he was trained to become a miner, and his first job in Austria was in a company that builds roads. However, he soon found a permanent position in this textile factory. He lives in a small apartment, owned by the factory.</ab>
